                        <note rend="inline" type="source">211.18/18: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Costa Rica</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Thurston</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">San
                                        José</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-01-21T11:00:00-06:00"><hi rend="italic">January 21,
                                        1922—11 a.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received January 22—5:25
                                p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>146. Department’s instruction number 53. Signed extradition treaty this
                            morning with the Minister for Foreign Affairs.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Thurston</hi></signed></closer>
